These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bongani, dannemann
3 different games are played: bridge, poker, whist
City: venice, hamburg, liverpool
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, van
 1. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person playing bridge is the cain-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the boat is the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the dannemann-smoker is between the owner of the goldfish and the person driving the van##2
10. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing bridge is the owner of the rat##1
12. the person playing whist is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Cigar          | cain   | dannemann            | bongani     |
| Game           | bridge | whist | poker |
| City   | venice      | liverpool               | hamburg        |
| Pet           | rat        | chinchilla         | goldfish   |
| Sport         | tennis     | skateboarding      | golf       |
| Transport     | van        | train              | boat       |

