.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra, chaman
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, orange, peach
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, indian, turkish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, trance
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, soccer, surfing
 1. the person eating kiwi is the turkish##1
 2. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 3. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
 4. the person eating peach is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person eating kiwi and the nigerian##2
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person eating orange and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 7. the chaman-smoker is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of trance is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Cigar      | game | alhambra | chaman        |
| Food          | orange   | peach    | kiwi        |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | indian | turkish |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | ambient  | r&b         |
| Pet           | snake    | hedgehog | mouse       |
| Sport     | soccer   | surfing    | swimming  |

