.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, tea
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, car, motorbike
City: marseilles, san-francisco, colone
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, entrepreneur, scientist
House: victorian, wooden, cape-cod
3 different pets are kept: cat, pony, rat
 1. the chef is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 2. the scientist is the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the wooden house is the person drinking juice##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person driving the subway is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the owner of the pony##2
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 8. the wooden house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
 9. the scientist is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is the entrepreneur##1
12. the wooden house is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Beverage      | juice        | 7up     | tea          |
| Transport          | car     | subway | motorbike    |
| City         | san-francisco    | marseilles  | colone |
| Job           | entrepreneur | chef    | scientist    |
| House   | wooden      | cape-cod | victorian      |
| Pet           | cat          | rat     | pony         |

