.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite
3 different games are played: billiard, go, bridge
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, soul
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, november, july
There 3 different types of food: apple, papaya, onion
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of d&b is between the person eating papaya and the person playing bridge##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating apple##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person playing bridge is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | sprite      | fanta        |
| Game         | bridge   | billiard     | go |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | documentary | disaster     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | d&b         | soul         |
| Birthday   | january   | july     | november      |
| Food         | apple  | onion     | papaya         |

