 7. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 9. the german is between the person who likes orange and the person eating cranberry##2
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
