.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice
City: edinburgh, paris, nizza
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, swisher, oliveros
House: ranch-style, futuristic, farmhouse
There are 3 different nationalities: british, german, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skiing, tennis
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the futuristic house is between the person traveling to paris and the nigerian##2
3. the british is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
6. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the ranch-style house is the person traveling to nizza##1
8. the person who's sport is handball is between the dannemann-smoker and the person drinking juice##2
9. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| Beverage      | juice    | iced-tea           | 7up         |
| City         | nizza   | edinburgh             | paris  |
| Cigar           | oliveros  | swisher | dannemann |
| House   | ranch-style      | futuristic              | farmhouse      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | german             | british     |
| Sport         | skiing   | handball           | tennis      |

