.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, potato, spinach
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, pink, amber
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, mexican
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, old-henry, aristoff
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, paramedic, coach
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter
 1. the argentine is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 3. the person driving the car is on the right of the police-officer##1
 4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 5. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
 8. the mexican is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 9. the person who likes pink is the person eating potato##1
10. the coach is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |
| Food          | potato    | spinach  | peach   |
| Color   | pink      | light-blue  | amber  |
| Nationality   | argentine | chinese  | mexican |
| Cigar           | old-henry     | cain   | aristoff   |
| Job         | police-officer  | paramedic | coach |
| Transport     | scooter   | car      | roller  |

