.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-20::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, pumpkin, watermelon
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, apricot, lilac
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, poppy, lily
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, cain, game
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, thai
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, water-polo
 1. the person who likes apricot is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 3. the game-smoker is the person eating potato##1
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is in an even position##4
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growslily is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
10. the person who growspoppy is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Food          | pumpkin     | watermelon   | potato     |
| Color         | lilac | aquamarine   | apricot  |
| Flower           | amaryllis   | lily | poppy   |
| Cigar   | pall-mall    | cain       | game    |
| Nationality   | thai        | colombian    | japanese   |
| Sport         | rowing      | biathlon     | water-polo |

 